  "summary": "ps_checkout allows unauthorized method invocation through unvalidated parameter",
  "details": "### Impact\n\nUnvalidated parameter can lead to some unauthorized method invocation with very little possibilities.\n\n### Patches\n\nThe problem has been patched in versions\n\n- v5.3.0 for PrestaShop 1.7 (build number: 7.5.3.0)\n- v5.3.0 for PrestaShop 8 (build number: 8.5.3.0)\n- v5.3.0 for PrestaShop 9 (build number: 9.5.3.0)\n\nRead the [Versioning policy](https://github.com/PrestaShopCorp/ps_checkout/wiki/Versioning) to learn more about the build numbers.\n\n### Credits\n\nPrestaShop thanks [PATICEO](https://www.paticeo.com/) for reporting the issue.",
